&lt;li&gt;Experience managing customer engagements from start to finish, including planning, execution, and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management skills and ability to prioritize multiple tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Change management and problem-solving experience&lt;/li&gt;
